Package: phaserR
Title: An R Interface to the Phaser.js Game Framework
Version: 0.0.0.9015
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Maciej", 
      family = "Banas", 
      email = "banasmaciek@gmail.com", 
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: This package provides an R-based API to build and control 2D games 
  using the Phaser.js JavaScript engine. It enables integration with Shiny 
  applications, allowing R developers to create interactive games and
  simulations using a declarative R syntax.
